stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unsaved : new_diagram()
    Unsaved --> Saved : save_diagram() / save_diagram_as()
    Saved --> Modified : edit / move / delete (modified = True)
    Modified --> Saved : save_diagram()
    Saved --> Unsaved : new_diagram()
    Modified --> Unsaved : new_diagram() (after prompt)
    Saved --> [*] : exit
